2025-11-21IRCCImmigration and Refugee Protection ActRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection RegulationsRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations in order to add Qatar to the list of countries and territories whose citizens are exempt from the temporary resident visa requirement and eligible to apply for an electronic travel authorization for travel to Canada.Registration: SOR/2025-0234 Publication Date: 2025-12-03
subject: Regulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
precis: Regulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations in order to add Qatar to the list of countries and territories whose citizens are exempt from the temporary resident visa requirement and eligible to apply for an electronic travel authorization for travel to Canada.
